# Build / IDE / VCS artefacts — never needed inside the image
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/publish/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/.dockerignore
**/Dockerfile
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.userosscache
**/*.sln.docstates

# OS cruft
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/ehthumbs.db
**/Desktop.ini

# Tests are not built or shipped by the image
tests/

# Docs & planning artefacts
docs/

# Local env / secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/appsettings.*.local.json
**/*.secrets.json

# Node stuff (if ever added)
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
